{
  "stem": "17625.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 213.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in another kommando was Kaminski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You heard about Kaminski?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- he was also a nice-- a-- a Jewish kapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had crematorium two, three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- he had-- in his commando he had [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A whole selection of those people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he gave them the hair selection, a special job to collect the hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they-- they-- he didn't want them to-- to-- to work on the other things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So where was I then, there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were talking about the doctors and the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The dentists.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Kaminski took these group of Hasidic young men?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah. yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he put him up for the special job there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the dentist, by the end of it I'll-- I'll come-- I have to jump from one thing to the other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The end of the dentist was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that when the [NON-ENGLISH] was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what it means, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our-- our world.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took their lives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took their own lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they-- they had-- they kept him there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no way out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you smelled sonderkommando, this was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You couldn't go out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what-- they took-- they took-- they took their own-- their own-- their own lives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they fell into sonderkommando, as dentists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the-- what the dentist did, they melt-- they melt the teeth what this Epstein pulled out, who was this-- this-- this-- pull-- pull-- he was a tooth puller.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And took out-- he put it in a-- in a basket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS came and took this basket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they melted it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
